    'aid' => '39',
    'catid' => '13',
    'typeid' => '0',
    'title' => '<font style="color:;">报国寺隆重举行盂兰盆孝亲追思法会</font>',
    'tag' => NULL,
    'username' => 'admin',
    'userid' => '1',
    'view' => '11',
    'color' => NULL,
    'strong' => '0',
    'toppost' => '0',
    'font' => '',
    'spid' => '0',
    'ip' => '',
    'mtitle' => NULL,
    'keyword' => NULL,
    'description' => NULL,
    'listorder' => '2108',
    'adddate' => '2016-08-17',
    'author' => 'admin',
    'image' => '/',
    'thumb' => '/upload/images/201304/2108.jpg',
    'state' => '1',
    'checked' => '1',
    'introduce' => '为庆祝这一传统节日，水神山报国寺隆重举行盂兰盆孝亲追思法会，劝导世人重视孝道、知父母恩、报父母恩。',
    'introduce_len' => '0',
    'content' => '<p style="white-space: normal;"><span style="color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 18px;">2016年8月17日（农历七月十五），是佛教传统的盂兰盆节，又称为佛欢喜日。为庆祝这一传统节日，水神山报国寺隆重举行盂兰盆孝亲追思法会，劝导世人重视孝道、知父母恩、报父母恩。</span></p><p style="white-space: normal;"><span style="color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 18px;"><br/></span></p><p style="white-space: normal;"><span style="color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 18px;">大殿内梵音环绕，供果飘香。报国寺僧众及十方信众排班肃立，法师与居士共同诵持《佛说盂兰盆经》，并举行了普佛上供、消灾免难、瑜伽焰口施食等佛事活动。</span></p><p style="white-space: normal;"><span style="color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 18px;"><br/></span></p><p style="white-space: normal;"><span style="color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 18px;">法会期间佛号长诵，梵音呗唱，法师虔诚诵读经典，清净优雅的诵经声吸引了众多信众及游客，他们听闻经声，纷纷加入到法会当中，在法师们的带领下诵经祈福，超度先亡，感念佛陀恩德、父母恩德。法会清静庄严，圆满殊胜。</span></p><p style="white-space: normal;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 18px;"><br/></span></p><p style="white-space: normal;"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">此次盂兰盆孝亲追思法会持续了七天，信众们在这欢喜的日子里焚香点灯，祈福、思亲。<br/></span></p><p style="white-space: normal;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);"><br/></span></p><p style="white-space: normal;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);"></span></p><p style="white-space: normal; text-align: center;"><img src="/upload/images/201701/14840627585473.jpg" title="14840627585473.jpg"/></p><p style="white-space: normal;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);"><br/></span></p><p style="white-space: normal; text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);"><img src="/upload/images/201701/14840627581122.jpg" title="14840627581122.jpg"/></span></p><p style="white-space: normal;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);"><br/></span></p><p style="white-space: normal;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);"></span></p><p style="white-space: normal; text-align: center;"><img src="/upload/images/201701/14840627583777.jpg" title="14840627583777.jpg"/></p><p style="white-space: normal; text-align: center;"><img src="/upload/images/201701/14840627586848.jpg" title="14840627586848.jpg"/></p><p style="white-space: normal;"><br/></p><p style="white-space: normal; text-align: center;"><img src="/upload/images/201701/14840627585868.jpg" title="14840627585868.jpg"/></p><p style="white-space: normal;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;">延伸阅读：盂兰盆节，又称中元节。“盂兰”，倒悬的意思，倒悬形容苦厄之状，盆是指盛供品的器皿。佛教认为供此具可解救已逝去父母、亡亲的倒悬之苦。佛陀教民众在七月十五日做“盂兰盆法会”，其福报可百倍。这功德不只可以救度现在父母，寿命百年无病，无一切苦恼之患，乃至七世父母离恶鬼苦，得生天人中，福乐无极。<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"/></span></p><p style="white-space: normal;"><span style="color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br/></span></p><div style="white-space: normal;"><span style="color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br/></span></div><p style="white-space: normal;"><br/></p><p><br/></p>',
